# how-i-did

1) add user in DSM control panel so that home directory etc is mapped

2) Install debian-chroot from synocommunity packages: 
https://markpith.wordpress.com/2015/10/26/debian-chroot-on-synology-nas/

3) Install Cloud Station for Dropbox functionality on home dir (on the NAS)

4) Install Cloud Station Client for Ubuntu on the debian-chroot

5) Install Cloud9 IDE (install-sdk.sh may take hours)

6) Download ARM build of `pgweb` and put in /usr/local/bin

